The paper deals with software development and verification, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The use of model-checking and testing techniques suggests a focus on programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also mentions the difficulty of establishing adequacy criteria for testing, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with systems that may be dynamically upgraded, which suggests a focus on systems and control (cs.SY).
